item.title: Client name above -- HUH?
item.dc:creator: @digzey digzey
item.description:
@digzey wrote:

Basically you want to change the client to be your own? - Well it is simple go though the client.java file of the client and find the name of the server (for example. Digzeyscape , press control+f and search for it. Although if it has a different color then it would be @gre@digzey@red@scape , just assign the colors to what it says.) As for the name of the client at the top that is in another file in which i cannot remember the name but it is distinctly different from the others. Just use the same process of finding using cntrl+f in notepad.(This time there is no need for colors uses)
